data.description: Welcome to Big Horse Ranch & Little Cattle Co. located in Ione. 40+ acres of truly a one-of-a-kind property that offers it all.  Current residence consists of a 2-bedroom 2 bath with office.  Steps away from residence is a spot ready to build your dream home. The land has gently rolling hills that is perimeter, cross and quarter fenced and 18 of the acres are irrigated with k-line irrigation.  Surrounding the property, you will find a 60x40 metal shop with 3 phase power and 2 roll up doors. Additional shop and 3 covered stalls. A 2-bedroom 1 bath bunkhouse with attached cut and wrap facility with office and bathroom.  This could be perfect for a hobby or to continue what the owner has started.  There are 2 wells on the property both refurbished a year and a half ago, storage tanks are 8,000 gallons and 3,700 gallons. 3-acre pond and a one-acre area with picnic benches and a firepit along the creek.  Two power drops.  2 separate entrances and 1,000 ft of road frontage. So much potential for this property in a prime location.
